title: [River's Rest, Festival Grounds]
description: A small wooden shack sits near the river's edge, with a short dock that juts out into the water.  Cattails and grass have grown up around the base of the shack, and dragonflies dance along the surface of the water, occasionally landing to rest on a reed.
